{"tha-ap286:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap286:0.2":"Pannadayakavagga ","tha-ap286:0.3":"Ekapupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap286:1.1":"“Dakkhinamhi duvaramhi, ","tha-ap286:1.2":"pisaco asaham tada; ","tha-ap286:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap286:1.4":"pitaramsimva bhanumam. ","tha-ap286:2.1":"Vipassissa naraggassa, ","tha-ap286:2.2":"sabbalokahitesino; ","tha-ap286:2.3":"Ekapuppham maya dinnam, ","tha-ap286:2.4":"dvipadindassa tadino. ","tha-ap286:3.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap286:3.2":"yam pupphamadadim tada; ","tha-ap286:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap286:3.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap286:4.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap286:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap286:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap286:5.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma ekapupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap286:6.1":"Ekapupphiyattherassapadanam catuttham. "}